title: For Sale:  Fostech Echo AR2 Trigger
postcontent:
The trigger is new. The Echo Trigger allows the shooter to select from 3 different settings
Safe Mode: Firearm will not fire.
Semi-Automatic Mode: Firearm fires when trigger is pulled.
Echo Mode: Firearm fires when trigger is pulled and also when trigger is released.
The Echo Trigger is designed with safety being the utmost priority. When the shooter is in the Echo Mode and depresses the trigger one round is fired, if the target moves, the shooter can move the selector to the safe position and a second round will not fire upon release.
 
The echo trigger has several distinct features
PATENTED Design that gained ATF Approval (Patent # US 8,820,211 B1)
Technology licensed through HIPERFIRE inside the Echo Trigger
Light, clean, and crisp pull in Semi-Automatic Mode
The Echo Trigger is packed full of cutting edge technology
Reliable function in Echo Mode

title: For Sale/Trade:  DSA SA58 FAL 308/7.62 Nato  PRICE DROP
location: Olympia, Centralia, Tacoma, Shelton, Olympia, Washington
postcontent: I have a nicely upgraded DSA FAL, this is not built from a parts kit like other FAL rifles, the DSA is built in the USA by a company that has an outstanding record for quality assurance.  It features a Magpul PRS stock with adjustable cheek weld height and length of pull, upgraded safety selector switch that allows you to activate it on and off without taking your hand off the grip, it has an upgraded trigger that is made by STEYR for a very light and crisp break.  it has a 18' barrel for accuracy, quad rail system, muzzle brake, and the DSA dead nutz top rail.  This rifle is built tough and dependable. it has a fully adjustable gas system that allows you to adjust the gas to many different types of loads to give you a very soft low recoil, and good for suppressor use. this is a piston driven system, it keeps the bolt and chamber clean and cool for many rounds of consisten trouble free shooting. it also shoots very fast, you can stay on target and unload with it really efficiently and accurately. video from speed shooter JM shows 19 rounds on target 3 seconds!  the charging handle is non reciprocating which is another plus. break down is very simple and you can field strip and clean without tools. this made it very desirable for militaries around the world, like the AK 47, simple reliable and easy to clean. The FAL is known as the right arm of the free world. over 90 countries adopted it as their military issue battle rifle.  The US went with the M14 (M1A1) out of favoritism for th designer, but its well thought that we may have won the Vietnam war if we had went with the FAL. My rifle has the Isreali designed bolt carrier plate you can see the grooves in the picture where the ejection port is. this design allows the weapon's action to clear itself of sand and fine debris which as you know tends to shut down many other types of rifles.  This improvement made the FAL truly dependable for all environments. It will come with 8 x 20 round magazines. The bipod pictured is not encluded but the quad rail allows you to attach what ever lights, lasers, bi pods and fore grips you need. the top rail holds true and zero.  The scope is also not included unless you want to pay for it in addition. sling is included.i have the original stock handguard, and buttstock for the rifle as well. (included)check out this videos of the FAL: search Youtube for:Colion Noir and the FN FALalso to see it shot unburied from a mud pile, and also draged through a swamp water look for FAL the First Black Rifle
